Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:47.27,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Veď si predsa spachtoška, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.19,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Zvyčajne vstávaš až poobede.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:52.94,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ako by som mohla vstávať poobede, keď chodím do školy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.40,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Už aj poď sem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:14.71,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Keď pôjdeme po tejto ceste, prídeme do Azabu-Juuban.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:17.05,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Je to blízko mojej kancelárie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:20.13,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Občasne tam aj ja chodím.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:22.30,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Predávajú tam {\i1}ningyo-yaki{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:25.68,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tam chodím aj ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:27.85,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Čerstvo z trúby chutia naozaj úžasne.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:31.81,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mohli sme sa stretnúť,\N aj keby nebolo zemetrasenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:36.07,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Teda, myslím, že ty a {\i1}sestrička{\i0} ste sa mohli stretnúť, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:39.28,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mohli sme byť všetci kamaráti.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:42.82,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.62,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Som si istá, že by sme nimi mohli byť.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.00,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Zrútili sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:52.87,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:55.38,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prejdime pod nimi čo najrýchlejšie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:56.21,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:04:03.63,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama mi povedala, že to tu celé postavili, keď bola na výlete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.34,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nemožné.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.60,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ja to myslím vážne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:10.31,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ako to mohli postaviť iba za tri dni?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:13.06,M8-Notes,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Prvá správa dneška je aktuálna správa o ohni v Sangenjai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:15.77,M8-Notes,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Podľa doterajších informácii,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:18.98,M8-Notes,,0,0,0,,{\an8}po zemetrasení zachvátili areál stanice Sangenjaya v štvrti Segataya
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:21.99,M8-Notes,,0,0,0,,{\an8}obrovské plamene.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:23.95,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nebýva v Sangenjay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:26.16,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,...Mari?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:29.20,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Bývam dosť ďaleko od stanice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:33.16,M8-Notes,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ako ďalšie vám prinášame správy z Koenji;
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:35.33,M8-Notes,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Obvod Koenji v štvrti Suginami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:39.17,M8-Notes,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Všetky cesty vedúce do tejto oblasti boli zatarasené.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:39.17,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prosím, pripoj sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:46.72,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nefunguje to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.35,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A teraz vám prinášame správy o počasí.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:54.10,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hlásime sa priamo z oblasti Arakawy, v ktorej sa všetky hrádze zrútili;
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:55.14,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tajfún zanechal túto štvrť v—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:58.19,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Americká siedma námorná flotila v Tokyo Bay začala—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:04:59.94,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,A čo Sangenjaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:01.90,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ozaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:06.32,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prepáčte,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:08.95,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,je tu niekto?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:25.30,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,A to som si myslela, \Nže by sa tu dalo niečo robiť...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.30,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.06,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mala by si sa vrátiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:35.64,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nemusíš nás brať so sebou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:38.56,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ako by som vás mohla opustiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:44.44,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prepáčte mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:46.45,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Idem sa pozrieť do kancelárie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:02.13,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dúfam, že je Hina v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:03.67,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Aj ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:37.96,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Poďte dnu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.67,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Poďte sem, vy dvaja!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:40.98,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prestalo to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:42.14,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:43.77,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vďaka, Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:02.21,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Myslela som si.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:09.09,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Mari?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:12.22,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ak je niečo, čo môžeme pre teba urobiť...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.30,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,V pohode, ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:27.77,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hina...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:34.45,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mari?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.41,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Čo je?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.66,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.33,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sestrička{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:49.04,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ššš, niekto je tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:59.01,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Čo to bolo za zvuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:00.93,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Rýchlo. Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:16.41,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Čo sa to—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:18.16,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Teda, kto tu je?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:23.37,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:33.17,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mari, zobuď sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.26,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.34,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:43.10,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mari, čo sa stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:44.73,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:48.35,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Čo mám robiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:15.76,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:16.67,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Je čas na desiatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:17.59,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:23.89,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:25.06,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mami?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:28.44,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:29.27,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:36.44,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:37.95,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mami?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.61,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:44.33,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Zachráň ma, mami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:44.95,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.54,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.08,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.92,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hina!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:52.21,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mari?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.50,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.96,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mari!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:10:59.55,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.18,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,A-Aya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:06.22,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vďaka bohu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:09.64,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mala som o teba strach!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:12.40,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ako sa cítiš?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:17.40,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Kam šli tie decká, Aya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:20.86,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Šli von, ale povedali, že sa vrátia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:24.37,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ach, tie deti...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:27.58,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nemala by si vstávať, Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:30.54,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.17,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Bože.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:34.04,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Odpočiň si.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:35.54,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Som v pohode;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:37.55,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,iba som trochu smädná.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:42.01,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Poznáš tie deti?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:46.72,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Stretli sme sa v Odaibe, tesne pred zemetrasením.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:50.56,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ideme spolu domov, keďže to máme po ceste.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:55.98,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Povedali, kam idú?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:12:00.99,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vlastne ani nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:02.03,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:11.50,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dnes sme pocítili obrovské otrasy okolo 12:15.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:15.29,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Správy o škodách ešte neprišli;
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:19.50,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}prosím, držte sa ďalej od budov a vyvýšených ciest,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:23.22,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ktoré sú poškodené alebo zničené.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:26.72,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Budovy a cesty javiace známky poškodenia
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.72,0:12:30.02,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}môžu spadnúť...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:28.01,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem, Aya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:30.02,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,To nestojí za nič.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:32.52,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Si tu celý čas, Aya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:33.56,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:37.27,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nemohla som sa spojiť s ostatnými, čo mali roznášku,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:39.90,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,tak som na nich chcela počkať tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:41.78,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ty si ale starostlivá.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:44.95,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ale nie, to vôbec nie je pravda;
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:49.95,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Bývam sama a ešte k tomu dosť ďaleko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:54.67,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tiež som si myslela, že budem viac v bezpečí tu, než v mojom rozpadnutom byte.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:55.96,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, Aya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:13:00.88,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prepáč, ale počula si niečo o Sangenjay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:04.84,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Trápi ťa ten požiar, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:08.43,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Zachytila som len kúsok v správach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:09.85,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Rozumiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:12.81,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:15.77,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nie, to je v poriadku. \NMusíš mať naozaj strach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:22.36,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hovorila som si, že Hina bude \Nv poriadku, keďže je s babkou,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:24.74,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,ale potom som počula o tom požiari...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:28.70,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...prosím, nepribližujte sa k riekam a pobrežným oblastiam, pretože sú nebezpečné.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.20,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Opakujem—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.79,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Kto vie, či niekde hlásia o stave Sangenjayi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:36.00,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Správy o škodách ešte—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:36.96,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ozaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:46.84,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:58.19,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...a zvyšuje sa od ohlásenia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:02.82,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Škody okolo Tokyo Tower sú omnoho vyššie po jej páde zo včerajška.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:03.94,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mari?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:08.86,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Aby sme sa vyhli ďalším škodám, okresná správa vydala...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:08.86,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hina sa rada fotila.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:15.20,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Pri jej úsmeve sa jednoducho nedá neodfotiť ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:17.54,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:20.50,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nemôžeš sa nechať všetkým zaťažovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:23.21,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Si všetko, čo Hina má;
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:26.47,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,nebojíš sa o ňu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:33.39,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sa už o tie deti postarám,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:34.85,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,tak choď domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.98,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Bude to rýchlejšie, keď pôjdeš sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:43.02,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,450)}Mala by si sa poponáhľať.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:49.61,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Prinášame vám aktuálne správy o požiari v Sangenjay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:53.12,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Požiar od zemetrasenia v areáli stanice
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:56.95,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}neutícha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.12,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:58.12,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dávajú to aj v TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:15:02.33,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Požiar spôsobuje mnohé škody v areáli...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:04.88,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Šíri sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:09.22,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Som si istá, že by ti v tom obchode jednu motorku požičali, Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:12.97,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Pôjdem ti ju vypožičať, len aby si sa dostala rýchlejšie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:18.35,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.87,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Si v poriadku, Aya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.16,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.08,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mari, ty krvácaš!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.14,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hocikto, prosím, pomôžte!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:00.27,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ste v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:01.56,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vydržte!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:09.94,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mari, kam—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.20,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Idem pohľadať tých dvoch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:17.12,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nie, ja ich pohľadám,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:21.00,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,ty choď za Hinou, Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:27.92,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Aya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.76,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Počkaj na mňa v kancelárii.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:32.97,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tí dvaja sa sem môžu vrátiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:43.14,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:44.81,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:51.82,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.95,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:01.75,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Bože, kam mohli ísť?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:55.55,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prepáč;
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:57.84,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ideme príliš rýchlo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:00.80,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Môžeš ísť napred;
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.60,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,ja som pomalá.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.56,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Pozval som ťa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:07.27,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Čože?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:11.44,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Pozval som ťa! Nemôžem byť napred!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:47.10,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prečo myslím na toto?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:52.48,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:55.69,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nemôžem ich opustiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:02.16,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Povedz, {\i1}sestrička{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:04.70,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,myslíš, že táto motorka bude rýchla?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:05.62,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Kto vie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:08.79,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Určite to bude rýchlejšie ako chôdza.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:13.13,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Chcel by som navštíviť Mari, keď sa dostaneme domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:14.96,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Aj ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:20.55,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Stoj, ty trdlo! \NJe to príliš ťažké!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:27.14,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.18,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Som.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.15,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Pohnime si a prinesme ju Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:34.98,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:37.86,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Raz, dva!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:40.70,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:43.62,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ste spotení jak svine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:47.83,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vypožičali sme ju pre teba, Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:51.58,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Na nej budeš doma skoro hneď.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:53.21,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:55.75,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prepáčte, že ste sa o mňa strachovali.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:58.38,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ale mali by sme ju vrátiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:00.55,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:02.93,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Na nej sa môžeš vrátiť rýchlejšie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:06.81,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,My traja ale nemôžeme ísť na jednej motorke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:23.24,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dávajte na seba pozor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:26.53,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ale myslím, že budete v poriadku, keď je s vami Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:29.91,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Na čas tu zostanem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:32.46,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prosím, pokojne sa vráťte, ak sa niečo stane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:33.79,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,To isté platí aj o vás dvoch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:37.04,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hoci nemôžem povedať, že by ste tu boli vítaní.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.76,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vyzerá to tak, že bude pršať.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:47.72,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Si si istá, Mari?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:49.97,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Som.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:52.39,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hina je určite v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:55.02,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama na ňu dáva pozor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:55.73,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:00.19,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Máš pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:01.23,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Určite to tak bude.
